{{Canceled|adventures}}
'''''SpecForces: Instant Adventures''''' was to have been a [[West End Games]] RPG supplement, written by [[Pablo Hidalgo]] and [[S. John Ross]]. In Hidalgo's words:
:''"The WEG [[Instant Adventures]] book proved popular enough to spawn a sequel, a [[Lords of the Expanse]] edition of IA. The second sequel would be instant adventures centered around [[Alliance Special Forces/Legends|SpecForce]] type characters. I was in the middle of writing a story about [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] commandos escorting an influential prince returning to his homeworld, and protecting him from [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperials]] and traitors."''

